          <div class="card-body">
            <p class="card-text">Have you ever accidentally opened a file in the wrong application and panicked? Little did you know you just unlocked a new databending skill! Databending is the process of manipulating a media file of a certain format in a software designed to edit files of another format. Artists have figured out how to percisely manipulate and delicately corrupt data without breaking the file.</p><br>
            <p>Glitch Art is a visual style artform that utilizes databending. It is characteried by using digital and analog errors for asthetic purposes and exposes a medium for expression and creativity in electronic technologies.</p>
          </div>
